Embedded Chat

Add an embedded chat window to your company website for customers to get quick answers to their questions while browsing your pages. Include a pre-chat form to collect key information and customize the experience to match your branding.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with Service Cloud or Sales Cloud

IMPORTANT The legacy chat product is scheduled for retirement on February 14, 2026, and is in maintenance mode until then. During this phase, you can continue to use chat, but we no longer recommend that you implement new chat channels.

The chat window sits unobtrusively on your web page. When customers want to chat, they click the button to launch. Add a pre-chat form for customers to complete, which helps agents gather basic information like their contact details, before the conversation.

Set Up Your Embedded Chat Window
Ensure that your org meets the following prerequisites before setting up Embedded Chat. Follow these steps to configure the embedded chat window and add to your web pages.
